Use the standard library
This is how to closest_integer of value:
   Remember that text is value
   When isarray of value, then:
      Remember that text is tostring of value
   End when

   Remember that number is tofloat of text
   Remember that lower is toint of number
   Remember that upper is sum of lower and 1
   Remember that lower_diff is abs of (diff of number and lower)
   Remember that upper_diff is abs of (diff of upper and number)

   When lower_diff is at least upper_diff, then:
      The answer is lower
   But, if not:
      The answer is upper
   End when
Now you know